        <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
        <p>
            Founded in 2016 in the historic city of Dumraon, Bihar, HealthAxis Hospital has been a trusted name in
            advanced healthcare, compassion, and medical innovation. Built with a vision to provide world-class
            treatment close to home, HealthAxis brings together cutting-edge technology, skilled doctors, and a
            patient-first approach that truly makes a difference in people’s lives.

            Our hospital offers specialized care across multiple departments including Cardiology, Dermatology,
            Oncology, Gynecology, and Pediatrics, Orthopedics, each equipped with state-of-the-art facilities and led by
            experienced medical professionals dedicated to excellence. We take pride in offering not just treatment, but
            personalized care that focuses on healing the body, mind, and spirit.

            Over the years, HealthAxis has grown into a symbol of trust and quality healthcare in Bihar. From preventive
            check-ups to complex surgeries, we combine expertise with empathy to ensure every patient receives the best
            possible outcome. Our mission is simple — to make advanced, affordable, and accessible healthcare a reality
            for every individual.

            At HealthAxis, your health is our priority, your comfort is our promise, and your trust is our strength.
        </p>
    </section>

